    <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" width="100%">
    <tr>
        <td id="descriptionArea">
            <p><b>Vision:</b> Provide ACI service department store associates with a simple digital interface to capture in-store customer orders efficiently.</p>

<p><b>What problem are we solving:</b> Store associates currently rely on paper-based forms for taking catering and/or cakes orders from walk-in customers in Bakery &amp; Deli departments.These forms are stored and used for daily order planning within the respective depts. </p>

<p><b>Initiative Overview:</b> <a href="https://rxsafeway.sharepoint.com/:p:/r/sites/Omnichannel/Shared%20Documents/3.%20Projects%20_%20Pilots/In-Store%20Digitization/In-Store%20Digitization%20of%20Orders%20KickOff.pptx?d=w2a654ac102a84e83b736e91f081e7029&amp;csf=1&amp;web=1&amp;e=KB8Frw" class="external-link" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">In-Store Digitization of Orders KickOff.pptx</a></p>

<p><b>Architecture:</b> <a href="https://confluence.safeway.com/pages/viewpage.action?pageId=601373704&amp;spaceKey=DPIM&amp;title=Solution%2BArchitecture%2B-%2BDigitize%2BIn-Store%2BLong-Prep%2BOrdering" class="external-link" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">https://confluence.safeway.com/pages/viewpage.action?pageId=601373704&amp;spaceKey=DPIM&amp;title=Solution%2BArchitecture%2B-%2BDigitize%2BIn-Store%2BLong-Prep%2BOrdering</a></p>

<p><b>How will digitization of in-store orders help?:</b></p>

<p><b>1) Customers</b> will be able to get order Updates communicate real-time updates on their in-store orders</p>

<p><b>2) Associates:</b> </p>
<ul>
	<li>  <b><em>DIGITIZE</em></b> High touch, high volume order entry filled electronically​​</li>
	<li> <b><em>Pricing &amp; ASSORTMENT</em></b>  tailored based on store​ in digital order forms​</li>
	<li><b><em>CENTRALIZED ORDER Mgmt.</em></b> Streamlined order queue for all ecom and in-store orders ​​</li>
	<li><b><em>Flexibility</em></b> orders can be edited, updated, or cancelled easily</li>
</ul>


<p><b>c) For ACI:</b> </p>
<ul>
	<li><b><em>Customer Insights</em></b> Better visibility into in-store customer orders​</li>
	<li><b><em>Consistent record</em></b> <b><em>keeping</em></b>  Maintain consistent record keeping for all in-store orders​</li>
	<li><b><em>Personalize &amp;</em></b> <b><em>UPSELL</em></b> Data driven insights to personalize and upsell, delight customer on their celebratory moments </li>
</ul>


<p><b>Which Service Dept. are in Scope?:</b> We will start with Bakery and Deli service dept.</p>

<p><b>What is the current process for in-store order forms?</b> Currently, bakery and Deli associates rely on paper based forms for bakery and deli, holiday meals orders. Current forms can be found <a href="#here" target="_blank" rel="noopener">here: </a> <a href="https://rxsafeway.sharepoint.com/:f:/r/sites/Omnichannel/Shared%20Documents/3.%20Projects%20_%20Pilots/In-Store%20Digitization/Order%20Forms?csf=1&amp;web=1&amp;e=kWgWiS" class="external-link" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">Order Forms</a></p>

<p><b>What is the proposed process for in-store order?</b></p>
<ul>
	<li>Customer comes to the store or calls the bakery/deli associate</li>
	<li>Associate uses ACI tablet (iPAD) to take the order digitally (instead of paper forms)</li>
	<li>No Payment info will be collected during order intake (Payment at POS at pickup)</li>
	<li>No Loyalty info collected during order entry</li>
</ul>


<p><b>Requirements:</b> <a href="https://confluence.safeway.com/spaces/CDT/pages/611350504/Q1+2026+Build+-+In-Store+Digitization" class="external-link" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">https://confluence.safeway.com/spaces/CDT/pages/611350504/Q1+2026+Build+-+In-Store+Digitization</a></p>

<p><b>UX:</b> <a href="https://www.figma.com/design/dBeyIoTJj2W259AeczVcsL/Digital-order-In-take-forms?node-id=786-14069&amp;p=f&amp;t=vUdrYZZyjya3XIfs-0" class="external-link" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">https://www.figma.com/design/dBeyIoTJj2W259AeczVcsL/Digital-order-In-take-forms?node-id=786-14069&amp;p=f&amp;t=vUdrYZZyjya3XIfs-0</a></p>

<p><b>How will we measure success of this?</b></p>

<p> <b>1) Engagement &amp; Adoption</b> - (goal is 50% of in-store orders digitzed)</p>
<ol>
	<li>Store/Dept. Adoption Rate​</li>
</ol>


<ul>
	<li>% using tablet for order entry​</li>
</ul>


<p><b>2. Data Insights:</b> Customer Order Customization Attribute Coverage to get Insights on customization of in-store orders​</p>

<p><b>3. Operational Efficiency:</b></p>
<ul>
	<li>Time taken per order (Goal = order taken in &lt;5 mins)</li>
</ul>


<p><b>4. Customer Satisfaction (CSAT)</b></p>
<ul>
	<li>Customer feedback collected via surveys</li>
</ul>

            <br/>
        </td>
    </tr>
